Renders reverse relationship rows for a SemanticSchemas dynamic display template.

Discovers all Page-type properties that have Allows value from category set to
the given category, then delegates to Category/reverse-discover for each property.

Only runs the discovery query when reverse relationships exist (count > 0) to
avoid empty whitespace output that would create extra space in the table.

Parameter 1: category name (without namespace prefix)
